data.description: Welcome home to this charming 2-bed, 2-bath gem nestled in Lakewood Park! Featuring a versatile layout, this residence boasts a 1-car garage with an additional room, perfect for a third bedroom or a cozy extra living space.Recent updates are plentiful! Embrace the allure of new with a fresh water softener system, pristine flooring, and a modern paint palette that spans every corner. Both bathrooms have been lavishly renovated, complementing the newly updated kitchen with its sleek countertops. A new privacy fence adds an extra layer of comfort and security. Key investments have been made for peace of mind - a 2020 AC and a 2018 water heater ensure comfort and efficiency for years to come.
